import React from 'react';
import { Form, Button, Dropdown, Container, Row, Col} from 'react-bootstrap';
import '../css/styles.css'

function FormComponent() {
    return (
      <Form>
            <Container fluid>
                <Row>
                    <Col>
                        <Dropdown>
                            <Dropdown.Toggle variant="success" id="dropdown-basic">
                                Select Change Type
                            </Dropdown.Toggle>

                            <Dropdown.Menu>
                                <Dropdown.Item href="#/action-1">Planned</Dropdown.Item>
                                <Dropdown.Item href="#/action-2">Unplanned</Dropdown.Item>
                                <Dropdown.Item href="#/action-3">Emergency</Dropdown.Item>
                            </Dropdown.Menu>
                        </Dropdown>
                    </Col>

                    <Col>
                    <>
                    <Form.Label htmlFor="inputPassword5">Team</Form.Label>
                    <Form.Control
                        type="id"
                        id="inputPassword5"
                        aria-describedby="passwordHelpBlock"
                    />
                    <Form.Text id="passwordHelpBlock" muted>
                        Please enter the 3 letter identifer for the application team.
                    </Form.Text>
                    </>
                    </Col>
                </Row>
            </Container>

        <Container>
            <Form.Label>Brief Title</Form.Label>
            <Form.Control 
                type="title"
                id='title'
            />
            <Form.Text>
                50 character limit.
            </Form.Text>
        </Container>
      </Form>
    );
}

export default FormComponent;
